# PowerEdge R740xd (gen 14, 2U dual-socket, 18-32 LFF/SFF drives, iDRAC9).
#
# UNTESTED — same caveats as R740. iDRAC9 BMC behavior likely similar to
# gen 13's clamp-to-safety but not verified. Default MIN_FAN=20 is
# conservative pending probe.
#
